Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:02.02,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Hello everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.02,0:00:05.10,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Um, {\i1}Mahou Shoujo Madoka{\fnArial Unicode MS\fs90}☆ {\fn\fs}Magika{\i0} final episode,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.10,0:00:08.98,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My Best Friend{\i0} audio commentary shall begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.98,0:00:10.44,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,With the role of Madoka, it's Yuuki Aoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:11.86,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,And—{\alpha&HFF&}...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.86,0:00:12.82,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,And—...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:17.37,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Um, I have come here again, it's Urobuchi Gen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:13.70,chiwa,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,0:00:18.08,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,And!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,0:00:18.08,umesu,,0,0,0,,Ah—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.08,0:00:19.66,umesu,,0,0,0,,Aoki Ume... is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.66,0:00:20.41,umesu,,0,0,0,,It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.41,0:00:22.58,others,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:22.46,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Cute! {\fnArial Unicode MS\fs100}＞＜{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.71,0:00:24.46,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,You're cute right from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:25.17,others,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.17,0:00:26.29,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,And!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.54,0:00:26.29,chiwa,,0,0,0,,And!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.79,0:00:26.29,otokomasturi,,0,0,0,,Ah—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.29,0:00:29.17,otokomasturi,,0,0,0,,Um, Series Director Miyamo–Miyamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.88,0:00:31.80,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Yes, I look forward to working with you—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.67,0:00:32.42,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,I look forward to working with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.42,0:00:32.42,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Look forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.42,0:00:32.97,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,And (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:33.93,chiwa,,0,0,0,,And with the role of Akemi Homura, it's Saitou Chiwa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.93,0:00:35.89,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I look forward to working with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.93,0:00:35.89,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,I look forward to working with you! *clapclap*
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:35.89,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Look forward~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:38.01,chiwa,,0,0,0,,So like this, on the final episode...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.01,0:00:39.10,chiwa,,0,0,0,,we feature the staff-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.10,0:00:39.89,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.89,0:00:43.27,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mou{\i0}, I don't know what to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.89,0:00:41.31,chiwa,,0,0,0,,{\i1}desu yo{\i0}~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.81,0:00:43.27,butch gen,,0,0,0,,It's a pretty big crowd, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.27,0:00:43.60,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ne~!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.60,0:00:44.60,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.60,0:00:44.14,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.60,0:00:47.56,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right before this, all the actresses gathered together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.98,0:00:47.56,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.56,0:00:48.31,butch gen,,0,0,0,,That's pretty flashy, isn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.31,0:00:50.61,chiwa,,0,0,0,,It was a set of {\i1}mahou shoujo{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.61,0:00:52.53,chiwa,,0,0,0,,What do we ask this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.53,0:00:55.24,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,What to ask, we can really ask anything, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.53,0:00:54.45,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.49,0:00:56.11,butch gen,,0,0,0,,What's coming my way? I'm a little bit fearful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.95,0:00:57.32,others,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.11,0:00:57.45,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:01:04.00,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Well, we're on the final episode, um, what do we ask first, Ao-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:06.04,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}I wonder what I want to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.04,0:01:07.71,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50.0)}I wonder what I want to ask~!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.71,0:01:09.38,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of things I want to ask, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.38,0:01:13.30,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,A lot of it is stuff I can't put into words correctly, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.84,0:01:13.30,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Um—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:18.47,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Was this type of ending-style for the final episode decided on from the very beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.30,0:01:18.47,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.47,0:01:23.22,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Well, for the scenario itself, there weren't any major alterations.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.22,0:01:24.18,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.18,0:01:25.44,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Um, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.44,0:01:28.06,butch gen,,0,0,0,,For the scenario itself, it was pretty much entirely used.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.06,0:01:31.77,butch gen,,0,0,0,,All together, there were a large number of canon-style scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.77,0:01:36.45,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Ne? Stuff like "A space with nothing in it" and "In space" weren't exactly written.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.69,0:01:36.45,otokomasturi,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.45,0:01:37.53,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ahh, is that right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.45,0:01:37.53,otokomasturi,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.53,0:01:40.07,butch gen,,0,0,0,,The ones who had a hard time were the people who made the content, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.53,0:01:40.07,otokomasturi,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:40.91,butch gen,,0,0,0,,(lol) "How's that?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:43.12,otokomasturi,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.91,0:01:43.12,chiwa,,0,0,0,,We have a person who here's really laughing about it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:44.16,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Nah, I have to truly praise them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:44.16,otokomasturi,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.16,0:01:47.92,chiwa,,0,0,0,,So then, what kind of feeling did that script have?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.16,0:01:47.92,otokomasturi,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.13,0:01:58.84,notes,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Unicode MS\fs55}笹木信作 {\fn\fs}(Sasaki Shinsaku) - Storyboard for episodes 4, 6, 10, and 12.\NBefore {\i1}Madoka{\fnArial Unicode MS\fs60}☆ {\fn\fs}Magika{\i0}, he was mostly known for work with Studio Ghibli, as the key animator for films such as {\i1}Mononoke Hime{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:52.00,otokomasturi,,0,0,0,,Right, well Sasaki-san created quite a bit of the content too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:55.09,otokomasturi,,0,0,0,,Well, um... it was basically like "What do we do? What do we do?" (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:55.72,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.72,0:01:56.97,butch gen,,0,0,0,,I'm truly sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.97,0:01:57.88,otokomasturi,,0,0,0,,Ah, I don't mind, I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.88,0:02:01.35,butch gen,,0,0,0,,I didn't make it easy on anyone, {\i1}mou{\i0} (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:02.85,otokomasturi,,0,0,0,,Nah, you gave plenty of guidance, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:04.89,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Nah, even if you say that... Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.93,0:02:13.23,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Somehow um, {\i1}Madoka{\fnArial Unicode MS\fs90}☆ {\fn\fs}Magika{\i0}'s {\i1}sekaikan{\i0}... including backgrounds and such, they're a bit unique, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.23,0:02:18.49,chiwa,,0,0,0,,They're different from an ordinary everyday style. Somehow, there are a lot of wide open areas, aren't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.94,0:02:17.99,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's right, ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:23.62,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Was that something that was understood clearly in the concept, from the beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:23.62,butch gen,,0,0,0,,That's right, ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:26.45,butch gen,,0,0,0,,The wide open areas are, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.45,0:02:33.96,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Well, the fact we wanted them was already established, but it was very unclear to what extent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:38.38,butch gen,,0,0,0,,For that part, really... Inu Curry-san had their influence in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:38.76,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.76,0:02:40.22,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Amazing, they're very charming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:44.39,chiwa,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mou{\i0}, t–this then white background comes, ne~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:44.39,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's right, ne!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:45.85,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Well, it has that "Final episode!" feeling, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:47.52,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Like "There's no opening!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:48.18,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Truly! Right, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:49.10,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Amazing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:52.44,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ah, then Madoka's final, um, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:57.36,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Her request, was it decided from the very beginning that she'd erase witches?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:57.36,butch gen,,0,0,0,,That's right, ne. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:58.28,chiwa,,0,0,0,,So that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:02:58.95,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ehh~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.95,0:03:05.62,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ah by the way, in everyone's opinion, do you feel that Madoka's final wish was "correct"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:12.75,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Well, that's right... personally, I don't think that it is mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:12.75,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Mm! Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:13.54,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:18.09,butch gen,,0,0,0,,For a middle school girl, it's a considerably significant thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:19.22,butch gen,,0,0,0,,That's what I think, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:17.38,chiwa,,0,0,0,,It's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:18.34,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's right, ne!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:20.80,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:21.26,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:23.09,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ume-sensei, what do you think about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:26.43,umesu,,0,0,0,,Really it's like "She really thought about this!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:30.60,umesu,,0,0,0,,She saw various things when tagging along to defeat witches, and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:34.73,umesu,,0,0,0,,She had a lot of various types of conversations, too, I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:41.36,umesu,,0,0,0,,Really, she came to properly comprehend various things within herself by thinking a lot, I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:42.70,umesu,,0,0,0,,It's extremely heavy, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.87,0:03:48.83,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Then somehow, everyone sort of gathers together like this to discuss Madoka's decision, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:52.04,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Was this like... companionship?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:57.88,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Well, that's right... she makes her wish, and then speaks with the people who have nothing to do with space and time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:03:59.80,butch gen,,0,0,0,,"Ah, this is very amazing!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:01.55,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ahh, I got the notebook back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:01.17,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Something like a final farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:02.30,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ah (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:02.51,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:04.43,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's pretty embarrassing for me, isn't it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:07.01,others,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:10.31,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Miyamoto-san, what do you think of Madoka's wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:12.35,otokomasturi,,0,0,0,,Ah, I think it's brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:15.77,otokomasturi,,0,0,0,,She doesn't really save the future of the world or the universe, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:17.86,otokomasturi,,0,0,0,,She's just saving {\i1}mahou shoujo{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:19.15,otokomasturi,,0,0,0,,I think "This is nice."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:21.28,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ahh, that's right, ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:23.15,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ao-chan, what do you think of it personally?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:24.53,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Always acting as Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:25.62,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.62,0:04:29.54,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,I think it's a wish that would've never happened without Homura-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:28.99,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ah, really? {\fnArial Unicode MS\fs100}♡{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:31.12,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Well, that's true from the standpoint of the {\i1}settei{\i0} too, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:31.79,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:32.46,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:33.87,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Somehow, this is... 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:41.55,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,A wish that couldn't have been done it weren't for Homura-chan's repeated worlds before this, and wanting to protect the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:46.30,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's why, it could be done by having someone as a companion who you trusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:50.06,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,I think so, so it's a pretty cruel, yet very wonderful wish, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:50.93,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:52.35,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,... Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:57.19,butch gen,,0,0,0,,When writing the scenario, I was wondering "Is it okay to write such a flashy thing?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:58.40,others,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:53.89,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,This part is amaz—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:04:58.02,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,(lol) That's!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:05:00.15,butch gen,,0,0,0,,It was a bit on my mind, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:03.74,butch gen,,0,0,0,,"Ehh, when they make the content what're they going to do? Mmm—!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:06.57,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Somehow they didn't become the witches of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:07.70,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:09.16,chiwa,,0,0,0,,She gives closure to {\i1}mahou shoujo{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.49,0:05:10.99,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Really, all the content I wanted was done...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:09.87,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ah, right right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:16.71,chiwa,,0,0,0,,But my first time seeing this, there was a conversation with everyone like "Ah, so there's actually tons of {\i1}mahou shoujo{\i0} around the world!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:14.33,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:19.88,chiwa,,0,0,0,,It isn't just a story limited to the bounds of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:21.50,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Nah, QB-san is world-wide. (WWQB)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:22.84,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ne~?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:24.09,chiwa,,0,0,0,,QB is all over the place, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:25.34,butch gen,,0,0,0,,All over. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.47,0:05:25.34,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Uwaaah~!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.34,0:05:27.26,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Scary~!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:27.26,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:30.26,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Then when you understand that everyone was fighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:34.60,chiwa,,0,0,0,,This, too, brings about a lot of thought somehow, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:34.23,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,It makes you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:39.02,chiwa,,0,0,0,,If it was just us fighting, then it'd sort of be like "Well, what about the rest of the world?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:36.73,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:42.90,chiwa,,0,0,0,,So it's like "Ah, I see, throughout the entire world everyone was fighting..."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:42.65,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ne~?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:45.95,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's an amazing thing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:48.41,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Then she saves them one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:51.03,umesu,,0,0,0,,All of the {\i1}mahou shoujo{\i0} of the past, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:52.74,butch gen,,0,0,0,,The past and the future, all of them, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:51.49,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:52.74,umesu,,0,0,0,,Around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:52.74,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:58.75,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,But somehow, you know seeing the {\i1}mahou shoujo{\i0} of the past, like Jean d'Arc... that deeply moved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:06:00.75,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,"So this does come!?" I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:03.88,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ne? You thought that might have happened, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:05.42,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I thought about it a bit, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:06.84,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,I think that is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:07.84,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:13.85,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,The art somehow gets sublime, it's deeply moving to me (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:16.02,butch gen,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yaa{\i0}, Madoka-san is doing some hard labor, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:16.77,butch gen,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:18.02,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Since she has to go one by one, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:19.31,butch gen,,0,0,0,,She splits up though, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:21.19,butch gen,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Iya{\i0}—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.48,0:06:28.78,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Mm, amazing I really love Ao-chan's warm style of acting here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:30.32,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Mm, so kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:35.75,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's right, I didn't want to overdo the {\i1}megami{\i0} feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:35.75,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\bord1.2\pos(1396,978)}goddess
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:39.08,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Somehow, I thought "If she were a girl, this would be painful."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:43.71,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Somehow, from a story standpoint I thought it might be good if she didn't feel too adult-like,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.71,0:06:47.38,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,I thought that the art would surely feel a lot softer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:50.72,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,I saw it was extremely soft and there was that bright light!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:51.22,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That image—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:52.18,butch gen,,0,0,0,,It worked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:53.35,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:54.35,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Then, that's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:57.10,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,It was time to stop being immature.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:58.52,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Did that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:01.69,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ya{\i0}, she suddenly becomes an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:03.44,butch gen,,0,0,0,,These frames have some pretty cool art, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:05.73,butch gen,,0,0,0,,It's quite moving, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:03.94,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:05.73,chiwa,,0,0,0,,It's cool, ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:05.73,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:07.03,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:07.03,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Truly~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:10.07,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Somehow, you know... I had really wanted to see this sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.07,0:07:10.95,others,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.95,0:07:12.74,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,She has such a {\i1}megami{\i0}-feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:13.49,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:17.50,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Homura-chan is constantly bleeding though (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:18.45,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,It's flowing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:19.21,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:22.63,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Somehow, Homura is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.63,0:07:29.01,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Um, before this, during the commentary with everyone, all of the actresses, I didn't get to talk about this enough, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:35.68,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Really in episode 11, I had that feeling of "It's the first time Homura has confessed to Madoka!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:39.98,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Those long lines about "I came from the future, you know."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:42.56,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}really{\i0} love that part.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:48.53,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Then, the Homura that I had been doing up until that point said everything there...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:52.78,chiwa,,0,0,0,,But really Homura is Homura, and her words would stop mid sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:53.24,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's right, ne~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:54.37,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Somehow it's like dot dot dot [...].
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:56.12,butch gen,,0,0,0,,And she does that hug, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:55.16,chiwa,,0,0,0,,"You are..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:56.12,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:57.79,chiwa,,0,0,0,,"To me, you are..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:07:58.74,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That dot dot dot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:08:01.54,chiwa,,0,0,0,,So it's like "Just say it!", but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:08.67,chiwa,,0,0,0,,She can't just say it, that Homura's feelings... I felt like they all came out right there, after so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:13.38,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Anyways, somehow it's really... personally, somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:20.14,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I think that probably Homura conveyed everything that she wanted to. Maybe not all by words, but she conveyed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:25.65,chiwa,,0,0,0,,So then, surely, Madoka chose this type of end...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:31.69,chiwa,,0,0,0,,She was trusting Homura in doing so. There is cruelty in it, but she was leaving the future to Homura...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:34.16,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Somehow, amazing, I feel like that requires more trust than anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.16,0:08:36.03,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Somehow, it's like "You're my beloved!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:36.66,others,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:39.54,chiwa,,0,0,0,,It sort of has that feeling though. Regarding that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:41.12,chiwa,,0,0,0,,how was the feeling in that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:48.29,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Right, it was originally thought that this will end as a "Madoka and Homura" story, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:51.51,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Especially around episode 10 that's true, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:59.97,umesu,,0,0,0,,The thing from just before, the words that Homura uses in episode 11 where she conveys everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:01.47,umesu,,0,0,0,,Then just after this, Madoka is like...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:06.19,umesu,,0,0,0,,"Everything... truly." Where she able to see everything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:08.36,umesu,,0,0,0,,During that moment, I was happy (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:09.86,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:12.40,chiwa,,0,0,0,,"Thank goodness!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:12.40,others,,0,0,0,,Good for you, Homura!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:13.94,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I certainly thought that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:13.11,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.94,0:09:15.28,chiwa,,0,0,0,,This clothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:16.86,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Cute! {\fnArial Unicode MS\fs100}＞＜{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:23.12,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's right, truly when everyone saw this... it was deeply moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:23.12,butch gen,,0,0,0,,For that design,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:27.37,butch gen,,0,0,0,,we had worries if it'd be okay since it only makes an entrance once, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:28.88,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Afterwards it became quite an existence, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:30.67,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Amazing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:31.38,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Just from that one cut, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:33.01,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's cause it's Hyper Ultimate Madoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:33.63,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:35.26,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,I was moved just from the screenplay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:36.84,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That was written there, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:39.97,butch gen,,0,0,0,,I might have had something to do with that, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:43.31,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,No, no, when I saw that, I was like "What's that going to be like!?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:36.26,otokomasturi,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:46.10,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,When I saw the {\i1}settei{\i0} scenario I was like   {\fnMona\fs60}( ﾟ∀ﾟ)ﾉ{\fn\fs} UWAAAA~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:47.73,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Then after the actual thing I was like   {\fnMona\fs60}ヾ( ﾟДﾟ)ﾉ゛{\fn\fs} HUWAAAAA!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:48.77,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:52.19,butch gen,,0,0,0,,That skirt is like a whole universe, huh? (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:55.28,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,There's a whole world under that skirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:52.40,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Everyone really, really wanted to see that, at the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:56.24,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:10:02.91,umesu,,0,0,0,,Somehow, seeing "Hyper Ultimate Madoka" in the {\i1}settei{\i0}, it was something like the ultimate weapon Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.87,0:10:00.24,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:02.87,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:02.87,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right, ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:05.37,butch gen,,0,0,0,,It was left there when I was writing eccentrically, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:07.71,butch gen,,0,0,0,,It was quite like "This is it."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:10.71,chiwa,,0,0,0,,How did the staff work with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:09.08,others,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:12.88,chiwa,,0,0,0,,How did you know what to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:16.80,chiwa,,0,0,0,,What was it? How was it decided to be like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:19.43,otokomasturi,,0,0,0,,The design was done by Aoki-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.43,0:10:19.84,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:20.59,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.59,0:10:21.72,umesu,,0,0,0,,The clothing, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:25.06,umesu,,0,0,0,,Like the clothing and that hairstyle, and the colors and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:27.27,umesu,,0,0,0,,I just did what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:30.69,umesu,,0,0,0,,I thought it might be troublesome when actually animating...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:32.90,umesu,,0,0,0,,But I was told to do as I pleased, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.90,0:10:34.44,umesu,,0,0,0,,What's this, was it troublesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:37.32,otokomasturi,,0,0,0,,That's right, Kishida-san really gave it his all, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:42.87,otokomasturi,,0,0,0,,It was like "how to do this part?" and "How should her hair flow?", Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:46.37,otokomasturi,,0,0,0,,He was constrantly drawing pages worth of sketches...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.37,0:10:47.66,otokomasturi,,0,0,0,,For just that one cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:49.08,butch gen,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:49.08,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,{\fnMona}（　・∀・）{\fn} {\i1}Hiii{\i0}!{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:50.46,butch gen,,0,0,0,,It's very extravagant, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:49.92,chiwa,,0,0,0,,{\fnMona}（　・∀・）{\fn} {\i1}Hiii{\i0}!{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:51.13,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Extravagant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:52.13,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:53.00,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Drawing that art!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:55.34,chiwa,,0,0,0,,This {\i1}kira-kira{\i0} scene with both of us, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:57.97,chiwa,,0,0,0,,During our after recording sessions, it had a leopard print design.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:10:59.63,others,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:02.01,chiwa,,0,0,0,,(lol) Really. It was like "So it's a leopard print design...?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.01,0:11:02.97,umesu,,0,0,0,,Like right here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:03.47,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:05.81,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Even though it was a leopard print design, it was supposed to be {\i1}kira-kira{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:07.31,chiwa,,0,0,0,,It was supposed to be {\i1}kira-kira{\i0}, right, Ao-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:09.31,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right, "shining" was written...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:10.90,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,"Leopard print?" (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:13.40,butch gen,,0,0,0,,In the final version, this will be a bit uncensored.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:15.27,others,,0,0,0,,Ohhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.81,0:11:15.27,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Half uncensored, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:16.94,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Is that right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:19.15,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Uncensored (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:22.20,chiwa,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mou{\i0}, for us, truly, somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:24.66,chiwa,,0,0,0,,The art acts as a guidepost.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:28.66,chiwa,,0,0,0,,So for us, during the after recording the art was acting as a guidepost...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.66,0:11:30.46,chiwa,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mou{\i0}, anyways...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:38.05,chiwa,,0,0,0,,It's just for a short time, but these two are able to experience each other's feelings, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:42.22,chiwa,,0,0,0,,At the end, Madoka is able to see everything, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:46.56,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Homura was somehow... properly still thinking of Madoka, {\i1}mou{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:48.72,chiwa,,0,0,0,,"What's with this!?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:51.23,chiwa,,0,0,0,,"Just how dedicated are you!?" I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:57.19,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,But she's doing such a kind thing, yet she's basically telling Homura-chan "You alone can definitely not forget about me."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:11:59.24,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,"Understand that!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:02.07,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,It's somehow very cruel of her, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:04.41,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,You might be able to think that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:09.50,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right. But, I thought "So the smile she gives is this gentle?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:11.50,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,It's relieving, isn't it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:12.96,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ahh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:14.42,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,(lol) Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:18.88,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I'm going to cry watching this, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:21.17,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Truly... somehow, ne...
