Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:55.33,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's right, she doesn't want her to forget about her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:57.67,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Isn't that actually more lonely!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:12:59.96,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:03.01,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's right, amazingly, ne...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:09.18,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I sort of feel like this was able to be done because of friendship between girls. Somehow, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:12.85,chiwa,,0,0,0,,During episode 10 I believe? I talked about this with Ao-chan a little bit, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:13.93,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:17.90,chiwa,,0,0,0,,If this were a {\i1}ren-ai {\i0}relationship, it would have changed a little bit, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:17.90,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's right, ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:24.19,chiwa,,0,0,0,,If this were a girl and a boy, I believe that they'd think of themselves a little bit more, like "I want them back!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.19,0:13:29.33,chiwa,,0,0,0,,But these two are constantly thinking about each other. Madoka in a bigger way, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.33,0:13:35.83,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Seeing that sort of thing, it's sort of like a girl's—Especially a main girl's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:39.84,chiwa,,0,0,0,,It isn't really putting yourself in a pretty place, but what to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:43.13,chiwa,,0,0,0,,It's like "She's a good person."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.13,0:13:46.30,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Conversely if they were guys, they wouldn't be together like those girls, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:48.80,chiwa,,0,0,0,,It'd have a bit more of a rough feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:51.06,butch gen,,0,0,0,,In place of that feeling, it'd be something like "GOOD LUCK!"
