Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:52.35,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:53.72,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Just like {\i1}Gurren Lagann{\i0}, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:55.73,others,,0,0,0,,(lol)
