Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:32.94,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.65,0:19:37.07,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Madoka did not erase curses themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:37.57,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:41.91,butch gen,,0,0,0,,And Incubator's thoughts of obtaining those were also left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:42.53,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.53,0:19:46.28,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Somehow I think that's extremely nice in its own way...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:50.54,chiwa,,0,0,0,,The fact it isn't entirely happy with everyone living in peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:51.42,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's right, ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.42,0:19:53.25,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Like there's still a bit left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:54.63,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Mm, that's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:55.75,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Well, that's right. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:57.75,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's really right, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.75,0:19:59.92,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Life isn't that pretty of a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:02.22,chiwa,,0,0,0,,It makes me sort of think that, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.22,0:20:05.60,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Conversely since it isn't essential for them to avoid each other anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:09.47,butch gen,,0,0,0,,It's okay for these two get along with their own rules in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:12.64,butch gen,,0,0,0,,So it's like that sort of thing is finally open to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:13.35,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:17.57,umesu,,0,0,0,,But this world's QB-san is really, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.57,0:20:22.45,umesu,,0,0,0,,He probably still makes contracts without telling people that their Soul Gems disappear, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:24.78,butch gen,,0,0,0,,I think he'd probably say it, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:27.45,butch gen,,0,0,0,,In short, that's why he says things to a careful extent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:29.12,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,I see, to say they disappear—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:30.62,butch gen,,0,0,0,,It's troublesome if you don't carry them with you, so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:31.16,umesu,,0,0,0,,Ah I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:32.62,butch gen,,0,0,0,,You might disappear from this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:34.88,umesu,,0,0,0,,In exchange for that, he will grant your wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.88,0:20:36.42,butch gen,,0,0,0,,That's right, ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:37.21,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:39.46,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:42.17,butch gen,,0,0,0,,It's still going to be necessary to put in some hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:44.68,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,He's still giving you hard labor, you could say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.68,0:20:45.30,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.89,0:20:46.64,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:48.81,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Amazing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.81,0:20:51.85,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That means that she'll continue to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:55.02,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I think she must be tired from fighting so much, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.02,0:20:55.69,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:59.15,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I think Homura was truly glad that Madoka was around!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:00.28,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Well, that's right, ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.11,0:21:00.90,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.28,0:21:01.23,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.23,0:21:03.11,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Well now, we're really at the end of the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:06.78,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Regarding this work, you can say whatever you'd like!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:10.58,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Let's hear what everyone has to say, starting with Miyamoto-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:15.87,otokomasturi,,0,0,0,,Ah... well I'd like to decide on season 2 as soon as possible. Right now people giving it their all until they die are helping with that...{なるべく早めに2期を決めていただけると、今一生懸命苦しんでる人達が助かるんで～}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:17.88,otokomasturi,,0,0,0,,While we still have staff that can work... {まだ作業してるスタッフもいるので…}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.75,0:21:20.67,otokomasturi,,0,0,0,,Please~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.88,0:21:23.34,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Then, as for you, Ume-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.76,0:21:27.05,umesu,,0,0,0,,I was really only useful until around the middle, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.05,0:21:32.27,umesu,,0,0,0,,This was a fun anime, and I'm really glad I was able to be a part of the design staff myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.27,0:21:35.73,umesu,,0,0,0,,Then, on the way a lot of really hard things happened, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.73,0:21:38.27,umesu,,0,0,0,,For that reason there were a lot of really helpful people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.27,0:21:42.86,umesu,,0,0,0,,I feel truly thankful for all of the staff-sama, and all of the viewers who watched. Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:43.90,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Yes~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:45.74,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Then, Urobuchi-san, give us some words, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.74,0:21:46.95,butch gen,,0,0,0,,That's right, {\i1}mou{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:52.37,butch gen,,0,0,0,,I've only just started writing for anime, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.37,0:21:58.33,butch gen,,0,0,0,,The fact I was given the ability to do what I wanted from the beginning makes me really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.33,0:22:03.42,butch gen,,0,0,0,,That's why to show all of the staff that let me do as I pleased my gratitude...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:05.84,butch gen,,0,0,0,,To repay everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.84,0:22:10.18,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Um, I'm frantically trying hard to think of the next thing.{あの、必死こいてこう、次の、あの頑張ってますので…}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.05,0:22:10.18,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Season 2!? Season 2!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.68,0:22:10.18,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Season 2!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.18,0:22:11.18,butch gen,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.18,0:22:13.01,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Season 2? What'll happen to Madoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.01,0:22:14.06,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ah, mamamadoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.06,0:22:18.35,butch gen,,0,0,0,,I think I can announce someday, but right now I'm frantically racking my brain.{まあ、いつかアナウンスも出来ると思うんですけども、今必死こいてあの、脳ミソ絞っております。 }
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.35,0:22:19.48,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll keep at it.{ええ、頑張ってます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.27,0:22:23.44,chiwa,,0,0,0,,It doesn't necessarily have a parallel to this world,{この世界のパラレルって訳ではないんですけど}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.44,0:22:25.61,chiwa,,0,0,0,,but surely there's a different type of ending, right?{違うEDもある訳じゃないですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.28,0:22:27.32,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Well, there's a lot that could be done, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.61,0:22:27.36,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That would probably have to be the case, right?{きっと、あった訳じゃないですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:29.66,chiwa,,0,0,0,,The possibility to see that kind of world...{そういう世界も見られる可能性も… }
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.66,0:22:30.57,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,How interesting~!{楽しみ～ }
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.57,0:22:32.83,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I feel that it hasn't ended here.{ここではまだまだ終われない感じですねぇ }
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.83,0:22:36.12,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I really want to see one where I can Madoka love-love...{まどかとラブラブが見たいです…!! }
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.12,0:22:37.91,others,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.91,0:22:39.46,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I want to be happy!{幸せになりたいです}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.46,0:22:41.25,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,I want to be happy~
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.25,0:22:43.21,butch gen,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yaa{\i0}... I wonder what to do.{いやぁ、どうなりますかね }
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.21,0:22:45.67,butch gen,,0,0,0,,I've shown Aoki-san a little of the plot, haven't I?{プロットまでは見せてるんですよね、蒼樹さんに }
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.55,0:22:46.59,umesu,,0,0,0,,Urobuchi-san doesn't give out happiness that easily, so...{虚淵さんはそう簡単に幸せにしてくれないから…}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.63,0:22:47.47,chiwa,,0,0,0,,AHHHHHHHHH
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.09,0:22:48.09,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,AHHHHHHHHH
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.09,0:22:49.09,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.09,0:22:49.89,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.89,0:22:51.14,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Well, that's right.{まあ、そうですよね。ｳｪﾋﾋﾋﾋ}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.14,0:22:52.30,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.34,0:22:52.05,chiwa,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mou{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.30,0:22:55.64,butch gen,,0,0,0,,No but, I was able to create happiness to this extent, you know.{いやでも、このくらいの幸せのうちは作れるんだぞ、というね、 }
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.64,0:22:57.64,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I have the proof for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:22:58.06,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.06,0:22:59.85,butch gen,,0,0,0,,I wonder if there'll be happiness? (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.85,0:23:02.65,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Well then, we're really at the end of commentary.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.65,0:23:03.15,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's right, ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.15,0:23:04.94,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I want to give our opinions too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.94,0:23:09.07,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I've truly said this time and time again...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.07,0:23:11.53,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Truly doing this piece of work and acting as Homura—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.53,0:23:12.70,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ah, Urobuchi-san thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.70,0:23:15.54,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Urobuchi-san's voice is the reason I was able to!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.54,0:23:17.04,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I'm truly glad for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.04,0:23:20.96,chiwa,,0,0,0,,To an extent where I don't think I've ever done anything that brought me this much happiness in my career as an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.96,0:23:22.38,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.33,0:23:23.96,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I think it's truly a wonderful piece of work, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.96,0:23:24.75,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ao-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.75,0:23:28.80,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,In doing Madoka, there was a lot of hope in a different meanings...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.80,0:23:33.60,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Somehow there was a lot of hardships and experinces to go through but none of it was bad at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.60,0:23:36.77,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,I think I was truly able to grow through doing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.77,0:23:39.77,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,I truly, truly love Madoka, magic, and this piece of work!'
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.77,0:23:41.52,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.52,0:23:42.77,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.52,0:23:42.77,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.77,0:23:47.03,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,So then, to everyone who cheered us on to the end, truly:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.03,0:23:49.24,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.03,0:23:49.24,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.03,0:23:49.24,butch gen,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.03,0:23:49.24,umesu,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.03,0:23:49.24,otokomasturi,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!